snippet.textDisplay: When I was watching the trailer for the song “Chal Chaliye,” I heard the sound of an engine in the background. At that moment, I was thinking that maybe this year, they would introduce a train station ambiance in the song, which would be quite challenging. However, the way they animated the train on the wall was fantastic. But guess what? In this song, they’ve taken it to a whole new level by having an actual full train on the set! Coke Studio always surprises us with elements that go beyond our imagination. 😊
